signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Ballcarriers with this ability have faster juke animations.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running curl or comeback routes.
Players with this ability have an increased chance to catch passes that have been tipped into the air.
Defenders with this ability have higher chance to catch uncontested interceptions, and they have unlimited stamina on the return (until using a special move or breaking a tackle).
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
